raw_analysis.raw_transcript: Okay, so I think technology in these days nowadays is nothing less than a blessing. And what's special about device, about this device is that it's totally based on artificial intelligence. So there are very few buttons and there is no touchscreen because a lot of us are right now habitual of touching our phones and because of this corona virus we were not allowed to touch each other or we were very cautious and sanitizing our hands. But this device even at that time there was no problem in using this because it is totally controlled by the voice and it as it is based on artificial intelligence you know you don't use your own intelligence and you just let it do it works and the thing is I first I earlier I used to have a clock next to my bed and it used to ring and wake me up but when the battery was low it would be a nightmare for me I would say because I was not able to get up on time and reach where I wanted to but since this I just tell Alexa hey Alexa wake me up at 5 a.m. in the morning and I don't have to do anything else, I just have to sit and relax and at 5 a.m. there's a very notorious alarm which is rang so that I can wake up and you won't believe the other day I was having guests over for dinner and there was a guy who was very old, I would say there was an old man and he was very surprised to see this because I told Alexa to give me a reminder that he needs to take his medicine. It was 10 p.m. I still remember the I mean, Alexa said, hey Robert, it's time for you to take medicines. He was shocked. I mean, he was happy and he was not believing it.
